{"word":"G2276 - ἥττον - hḗtton - hate'-ton - Less","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἥττον</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hḗtton</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hate'-ton</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Less</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"தீமைக்கேதுவாயிருக்கிற, குறைவாயிருக்கிற - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"less; for the worse, inferior"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Neuter of a compound of <b>&#x03B7;&#x0314;&#x0342;&#x03BA;&#x03B1;</b> <b>he&#x0304;ka</b> ( <i>slightly</i>) used for that of <a href=\"#/G2556 - κακός - kakós - kak-os'/2556\">G2556</a>; <i>worse</i> (as noun); by implication <i>less</i> (as adverb): - less, worse.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}